{
  "stem": "182.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 231.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was an-- a Pol-- a woman-- that I want to go there because my mother is there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And she gave me such a slap, and she pushed me back in the other row.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Now I always felt that she was cruel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But later, I thought about it, and I think that she was being kind to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Because she was there already many years and she saw, and she knew, that if the Germans will know-- will know that there is a mother and daughter, you know, they may all take the mother out, or separate us totally.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And she wanted I should keep quiet that that is my mother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Anyway, they took us to a barrack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "There were bunk beds.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Three.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Three-- I mean, two, one on-- no, three.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "One, two, three.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And there were 10 girls to a bunk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "There was one horse blanket on the bottom, and there was one to cover ourselves.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And they-- in the early in the morning, they brought-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And when we got there, the-- the Aufseherin-- that was the-- who took care on this group of people, and I think that there were about 300 or more in one bunk-- in one building.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "She told-- She t-- and the way the building was constructed, in the middle ran like a-- a-- it was supposed to be an oven to heat the barrack.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "There was never any fire in it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "But like in the begin-- in one end, there was like a chimney and where you could put in the fire.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And then this ran, made out of bricks, like-- how would we call it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was about this wide and this tall, and it ran the length of the-- of the-- the buil-- the-- the barrack.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
